page_title: 'Speech to text with Azure OpenAI Service'
page_description: Use the Azure OpenAI Whisper model for speech to text.
chunk_content: Prerequisites- An Azure subscription - Create one for free.- Access granted to Azure OpenAI Service in the desired Azure subscription.- An Azure OpenAI resource with a `whisper` model deployed in a supported region. Whisper model regional availability. For more information, see Create a resource and deploy a model with Azure OpenAI.> [!NOTE]> Currently, you must submit an application to access Azure OpenAI Service. To apply for access, complete this form.
